Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE FIVE COLORS OF LIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban, I see you have a mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother clamming up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason\NI shouldn't hear your voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai and Hyunckel are allowed to hear it,\Nbut I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears your silence is not\Nof your own choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we are again.\NJust like back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget how many decades ago it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nearly a century ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in Dark King Ban's\NSeventh Palace in the Underworld...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ron Berku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I should never have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron Berku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I hold you in very high regard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I would prefer if you would\Nserve me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kōmanotsue you made\Nis truly my greatest weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your other weapons are\Nalso magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,True masterpieces from\Nthe Craftsman of the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Kōmanotsue\Nthat let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If that thing is considered\Nmy greatest masterpiece,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,then it will quell my drive to create\Nthe ultimate weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose my touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now. Will you reconsider?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be Dark King Ban,\Nthe most powerful being in the Underworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can't bind my freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You are worthy of saying such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are strong enough to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're one of the greatest\Nswordsmen in the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know why you hide it\Nand work as a weaponsmith.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To be blunt,\Nnow that I possess the Kōmanotsue,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all that I want is\Nyour strength as a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the dark,\Nmurky sky of our Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle to bring\Ntrue light to it is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that, I want\Nas many powerful servants as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I offer you the position\Nof commanding such a mighty army.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is done. Farewell, Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. He will fight if pushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even knowing he cannot\Nbeat me in combat, he still defies me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd only kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But Darklings live a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he'll change his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see you're out for blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Ban's will?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-Why won't he dodge?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've insulted Ban's generosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I allowed that first strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This wound is my penance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you intend to continue,\NI won't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This man defied King Ban\Nfor his own freedom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why does he side with\NDai and the humans?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need any more\Nwounds from you, Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-He's fast!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. An ultimate Purification Spell\Nusing five Disciples.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To take down Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not going to just\Nlet you cast Minakator.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But we...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can at least hold him off\Nand buy you some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Mystban...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and Ron Berku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He came, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's evenly matched with Mystban?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He did singlehandedly\Ntrounce us after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! This is our chance!\NLet's get this over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,While the others are buying us time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow! Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that, and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona filled me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help clear out the riffraff\Nso we can cast Minakator!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the former Beast King,\NMr. Crocodine! Everybody salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good grief. I'm already "the former"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Crocodine, we have\Na new axe Ron Berku made for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine, swing that axe and cry out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Howl, Inferno!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Howl, Inferno!{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Ron Berku's special Great Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Inferno" casts Mera-type spells\Nand "Detonation" casts IO-type ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exceptional!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Howl, Detonation!{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Axe, huh?\NIt's like using my own Aban Strash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Garuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man, you can take it easy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll take you up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As if! I can't lay down for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merami!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're preparing for Minakator!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Amy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This execution stage is\Nright under Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect for the Circle of Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Everyone stand on the circle\Nand form a pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your Dark Armour Spear.\NRon Berku repaired it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks the same, but its attack\Nand defense have been greatly enhanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giving me the weapon\Nyou once took from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than you dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd fight without it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and live!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Amudo!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:10.54,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}GRAND CROSS{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.54,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}MEDOROA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered your words\Nwhile I was imprisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You glared at me and told me\Nto stop walking gladly into death's arms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your words made me want to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To grasp at the chance to keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was actually able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fight's barely started.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can thank me after we survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy, are you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to explain the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Amy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on your Insignias.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Minakator is a powerful\NPurification Spell on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But with Kiseiseki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With a pentagon of five Insignias of Aban\Nmaking a Magic Circle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the purification power is amplified.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it works, it should stop Ban Palace,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and nullify the magic field around it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It should allow us to invade Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do we do?\NDo we just stand here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one casting the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All you need to do is increase\Nthe power of your souls one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we do that,\Nthe light of our Kiseiseki should unite,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,creating a pillar of light\Nthat will reach Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A pillar of light...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll join hands going clockwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When you turn comes, focus your thoughts\Nand pass them on to the next person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the last.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,W-...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What if...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't gather the five lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the five lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Minakator will use only my Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably won't work on Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all nervous, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never done this before.\NDon't bother worrying... empty your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's do this then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Northern Grand Blade!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't move when you're in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Howl, Inferno!{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Nova!\NSo you've cut most of them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There's only a few left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Everyone attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Mystban, their boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's up there,\Nflashing every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a whole other level of battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Ron's quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh holy light,\Nwith thy blessed power...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,drive away the evil power of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is the pillar of light?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turn, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Amplify my thoughts...\Nand focus my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You should try emptying your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be easier that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! This blue light is\Nthe light of my soul, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Next is Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're evenly matched.\NNeither of us can win like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are those pillars of light?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They reach Ban Palace!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going nowhere, Mystban!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's... my turn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as I'm here,\Nyou're stuck sparring with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't interfere with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How very foolish, Ron Berku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think holding me at bay\Nwould give these humans a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NYou're suddenly very chatty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't want\Nme to hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have knowledge of the Underworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:19:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but hearing my voice won't matter\Nto one who will soon be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all going to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This disgusting laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's you, the Mystic Bishop Zaboera!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Army Second-in-Command\Nis my title now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Laboring for years can\Nsometimes yield such payoffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Save your prattle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't turn the tide of battle now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I'll give you\Nwhat you deserve at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera, this is your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as planned and wipe out the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me, Commander Mystban.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,These are Magic Capsules,\Nthe latest model of my Magic Cylinder!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Each can be loaded\Nwith dozens of monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And inside these ones
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,are powerful monsters that\Nnone of you have ever encountered before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all finished now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}G-Gods!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come forth, monsters of the Underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Derupa!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.99,0:21:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it wouldn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:12.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:18.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:23.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:29.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:35.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:41.84,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:47.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:53.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:59.27,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:01.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:05.19,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:10.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:16.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:22.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:30.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp's Insignia of Aban won't glow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Under Mystban's order, Zaboera unleashes\Na horde of Underworld monsters{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the Battle of\NLoroi Valley intensifies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With Minakator incomplete, nerves fray{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Zaboera's hand closes in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:23:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Peril of\Nthe Great Purification Spell"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.87,0:23:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:23:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:00.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,
